00:03:17.629 --> 00:03:19.830
of our great God,

00:03:19.830 --> 00:03:21.590
O Jehovah,

00:03:21.590 --> 00:03:25.030
everything we have done you have accomplished for us.

00:03:25.990 --> 00:03:27.949
We know that any success we enjoy

00:03:27.949 --> 00:03:31.110
is because of Jehovah's direction and blessing.

00:03:31.110 --> 00:03:34.310
And so the theme of this presentation is,

00:03:34.349 --> 00:03:37.469
see what Jehovah has done for us.

00:03:39.229 --> 00:03:41.389
The faithful discrete slave has always taken

00:03:41.389 --> 00:03:45.789
very seriously Jesus command recorded at Matthew 28.19.

00:03:45.789 --> 00:03:49.270
Go and make disciples of people of all the nations,

