00:04:06.469 --> 00:04:08.669
what was stated in the book.

00:04:08.669 --> 00:04:10.509
However, it was hard to know whether the truth

00:04:10.509 --> 00:04:11.949
was really touching their heart.

00:04:13.110 --> 00:04:14.389
With enjoy life forever,

00:04:14.389 --> 00:04:16.750
we're using a different method of teaching

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:18.750
that generates candid expressions

00:04:18.750 --> 00:04:21.310
by the students in their own words.

00:04:21.310 --> 00:04:24.310
This is just what the governing body feels is needed

00:04:24.310 --> 00:04:26.990
to bring new ones to dedication and baptism

00:04:26.990 --> 00:04:28.910
during these urgent last days.

