and 7,500 pioneers

01:04:11.260 --> 01:04:14.460
are preaching in almost 40 different languages.

01:04:14.460 --> 01:04:19.460
A special effort is made to reach Australia's native Aboriginal people.

01:04:19.460 --> 01:04:21.460
To assist those hungry for the truth,

01:04:21.460 --> 01:04:26.059
literature has been translated into some of the indigenous languages.

01:04:26.059 --> 01:04:28.260
Our Australian brothers and sisters

01:04:28.260 --> 01:04:32.059
have also found success preaching on passenger trains

01:04:32.059 --> 01:04:34.260
and at railway stations.

01:04:34.260 --> 01:04:36.659
This is the Broken Hill Station,

01:04:36.659 --> 01:04:39.260
a stop on the Indian Pacific route,

01:04:39.260 --> 01:04:42.059
which runs more than 4,300 kilometers

01:04:42.059 --> 01:04:46.260
or about 2,700 miles from Sydney to Perth.

01:04:46.260 --> 01:04:49.059
Many have learned the truth as a result of the preaching

01:04:49.059 --> 01:04:51.659
along this train line.

01:04:51.659 --> 01:04:54.659
Most of Australia's nearly 26 million inhabitants

01:04:54.659 --> 01:04:57.860
live in cities and towns not far from the coast.

01:04:57.860 --> 01:05:00.059
One of those towns is Naurah,

01:05:00.059 --> 01:05:03.460
home of the Naurah West congregation.

01:05:03.460 --> 01:05:05.260
With a little help from Zoom,

01:05:05.260 --> 01:05:09.059
the 80 brothers and sisters of the Naurah West congregation

01:05:09.059 --> 01:05:12.260
send you their warmest love.

01:05:12.260 --> 01:05:15.059
From the World Headquarters of Jehovah's Witnesses,

01:05:15.059 --> 01:05:17.260
this is JW Broadcasting.
